WEBVTT

00:02.200 --> 00:10.110
Today somebody came from India and told me
that, “You better change the name Sahaja

00:10.110 --> 00:11.740
Yoga into some other name.

00:11.740 --> 00:14.240
So I said, “What about Maha Yoga?”

00:14.240 --> 00:17.160
And he liked it very much.

00:17.160 --> 00:26.030
He said, “Now people are taking Sahaj Yoga
as their own and they are using it for their

00:26.030 --> 00:27.030
own purpose."

00:27.030 --> 00:29.160
I said, “Very good idea.

00:29.160 --> 00:32.730
If they are using it, is even better!

00:32.730 --> 00:40.460
Because the word itself suggests that this
union has to be spontaneous.

00:40.460 --> 00:42.850
They have to give a spontaneous union.

00:42.850 --> 00:46.090
If they claim it, they have to do it.

00:46.090 --> 00:49.520
If they are not doing it, then it is wrong.

00:49.520 --> 00:50.660
It’s very simple!”

00:50.660 --> 01:02.470
But he said, “In any case Sahaj Yoga does
not denote the dimension which it has reached:

01:02.470 --> 01:05.990
that people are getting en-masse Realisation."

01:05.990 --> 01:13.899
Moreover he said that people don’t understand
that the time has come for thousands of people

01:13.899 --> 01:15.740
to get their Realisation.

01:15.740 --> 01:23.350
Perhaps we are not aware [of] what time we
are born.

01:23.350 --> 01:26.939
So many people are seeking God.

01:26.939 --> 01:36.880
Never in the history before there was such
a multitude which was seriously seeking God,

01:36.880 --> 01:41.469
and honestly wanting to get their union.

01:41.469 --> 01:50.459
Only in the modern times you find they are
very honest, very sincere; and they are born

01:50.459 --> 01:51.459
seekers.

01:51.459 --> 01:56.829
I mean their quality is that they are seekers;
their temperament is that they are seekers.

01:56.829 --> 02:04.060
They are not satisfied with anything else
but seeking.

02:04.060 --> 02:05.319
Why this is happening?

02:05.319 --> 02:09.700
We have to think about it.

02:09.700 --> 02:13.680
Why people are not satisfied with what they
have?

02:13.680 --> 02:23.819
Why are they not seeking now the materialism
or the powers which are other than the Divine

02:23.819 --> 02:24.819
Power?

02:24.819 --> 02:30.569
Why do they want that they should know their
Spirit?

02:30.569 --> 02:31.670
What is the reason?

02:31.670 --> 02:35.280
Why such an upsurge?

02:35.280 --> 02:42.230
And why people, like mad, are following anyone
who comes across?

02:42.230 --> 02:49.060
To try every method and experiment with everything
to get that bliss and joy.

02:49.060 --> 02:57.340
You know [that], from ancient times, people
have been talking about your rebirth.

02:57.340 --> 03:06.329
Even at the time of Rama, one disciple called
as Nachiketa, went to the father-in-law of

03:06.329 --> 03:13.480
Rama, whose name was Raja Janaka, and asked
Him that, “Give me Self-knowledge."

03:13.480 --> 03:23.560
And Nachiketa was very, very anxious, very
much wanting to be the Spirit.

03:23.560 --> 03:29.549
But Janaka put him to many, many tests.

03:29.549 --> 03:34.010
And the conversation between them is very
interesting.

03:34.010 --> 03:39.879
So one individual is mentioned in those days
— I mean that’s a long time back, Rama’s

03:39.879 --> 03:44.079
time — who was seeking.

03:44.079 --> 03:54.400
Even at the time of Christ there was, we would
say, John the Baptist who talked of baptism.

03:54.400 --> 04:04.200
But as far as seeking is concerned, in the
multitude, there was no such urge, there was

04:04.200 --> 04:08.989
not that seeking as you find today.

04:08.989 --> 04:12.480
So there must be something in the atmosphere.

04:12.480 --> 04:17.670
Then another thing is that we are trying to
save time.

04:17.670 --> 04:19.290
We must have watches.

04:19.290 --> 04:22.630
We must see that [watch] after every ten minutes.

04:22.630 --> 04:24.490
Oh, we have to save time.

04:24.490 --> 04:25.490
We cannot waste time.

04:25.490 --> 04:30.310
I mean, supposing somebody has to go to India,
then a date is fixed, and then he must go

04:30.310 --> 04:31.960
by that plane, particular plane.

04:31.960 --> 04:35.500
If that plane is missed, he thinks he’s
lost the world!

04:35.500 --> 04:39.840
Time-saving is another urge within us.

04:39.840 --> 04:44.110
Why do we want to save time?

04:44.110 --> 04:49.390
Why this urge from the unconscious is so strong
that we must save time?

04:49.390 --> 04:52.330
Is there something going wrong or something
is going to happen?

04:52.330 --> 04:57.470
Or is there some urgency or emergency which
you feel in the time itself?

04:57.470 --> 05:02.540
Because, in the olden times, nobody used to
worry so much about time.

05:02.540 --> 05:06.200
So what is the reason for this kind of time-saving
today?

05:06.200 --> 05:13.650
We can see very clearly that there are genuine
seekers.

05:13.650 --> 05:16.471
There are seekers because of the faction around.

05:16.471 --> 05:24.260
And there are people who do not seek; who
are quite satisfied with whatever mundane

05:24.260 --> 05:30.380
life they are leading, or whatever ambitions
they have other than seeking.

05:30.380 --> 05:39.710
But the genuine seekers are so many in number
that we have to find out why this genuine

05:39.710 --> 05:41.960
seeking is working so much.

05:41.960 --> 05:48.770
And you are so restless about it, so anxious
that, without the seeking, you are not satisfied.

05:48.770 --> 05:55.600
You are willing to give up everything that
is on this Earth with you, or whatever is

05:55.600 --> 05:59.130
your own so-called possessions, but you want
to seek yourself.

05:59.130 --> 06:02.190
That’s a fact; it’s absolutely honest.

06:02.190 --> 06:04.740
There’s no doubt about it.

06:04.740 --> 06:08.270
But why there is seeking?

06:08.270 --> 06:14.290
It is because the Last Judgment has started.

06:14.290 --> 06:16.210
The Last Judgment has started now.

06:16.210 --> 06:21.320
Many great souls are taking birth.

06:21.320 --> 06:29.060
It is very common these days, you talk to
anyone about his child [and] they will tell

06:29.060 --> 06:36.350
two things: Either he is a grand old man,
some ancient figure born in the family and

06:36.350 --> 06:39.520
every word he speaks is wisdom.

06:39.520 --> 06:46.780
Or the other thing they may tell you is that
he’s a monster, he’s good for nothing,

06:46.780 --> 06:48.240
he is useless.

06:48.240 --> 06:52.060
Nothing in between!

06:52.060 --> 06:54.680
Now this happening also was very uncommon.

06:54.680 --> 07:02.660
Now we have seen, so many of you, who are
Sahaj Yogis, that so many children are born-realised.

07:02.660 --> 07:07.610
I mean, when I was born, I found very, very
few people.

07:07.610 --> 07:11.160
Except for my father I couldn’t find anyone
who was born-realised.

07:11.160 --> 07:19.470
And there were many fakirs and saints, who
came to our house, or we went to see them,

07:19.470 --> 07:21.470
and I found that their Kundalini was all frozen.

07:21.470 --> 07:24.810
They may be calling themselves saints or whatever
it is.

07:24.810 --> 07:31.430
But I was amazed that there was no companionship
with them because you couldn’t talk [to

07:31.430 --> 07:32.430
them].

07:32.430 --> 07:36.500
They were at a very low level of evolution
and they were just trying to make money or

07:36.500 --> 07:42.630
give some sort of technique or some sort of
a blah, blah, blah.

07:42.630 --> 07:46.150
Even then it was so.

07:46.150 --> 07:53.420
But innately in a country like India people
know what to seek, what to find.

07:53.420 --> 08:03.840
Now, because of your righteous life in previous
births, I believe, maybe, or whatever it is:

08:03.840 --> 08:11.560
as a blessing of that you are born in these
countries where there is affluence, where

08:11.560 --> 08:17.180
your attention does not go to material things
so much, but to higher things.

08:17.180 --> 08:22.150
And then you start thinking that all this
is a waste, a junk and we are not going to

08:22.150 --> 08:24.200
carry the junk of our parents on our heads.

08:24.200 --> 08:30.600
Some sort of feeling crawls up and you start
seeking.

08:30.600 --> 08:38.900
In England I don’t know how many children
I have seen who are born-realised, of a very

08:38.900 --> 08:39.900
high quality.

08:39.900 --> 08:44.460
Such great souls are taking birth on this
Earth.

08:44.460 --> 08:46.570
Why?

08:46.570 --> 08:48.030
It never happened before.

08:48.030 --> 08:55.740
And within these ten years’ time, such a
tremendous in-flow of these great souls is

08:55.740 --> 09:02.900
felt that one has to realise that there is
a kind of an emergency.

09:02.900 --> 09:12.050
This emergency is felt also even in those
people who are not yet seeking.

09:12.050 --> 09:17.580
They are so speedy; they are so anxious; they
get into stress and they get into tensions.

09:17.580 --> 09:21.860
If you ask your forefathers who had gone out
to wars: they never had tensions.

09:21.860 --> 09:25.730
They would kill ten people and sleep off nicely
without thinking about it.

09:25.730 --> 09:31.530
They didn’t even have the sensitivity that
you have, that compassion and that understanding.

09:31.530 --> 09:40.030
With this growth within, or we can say, with
this urge within, also there are many things

09:40.030 --> 09:47.950
that have happened outside that you can see
very clearly: is that a consciousness has

09:47.950 --> 10:02.670
come, a collective awareness has come, as
to the idea of cruelty, wars and also domination

10:02.670 --> 10:05.400
of other people.

10:05.400 --> 10:10.141
Perhaps none of you could be as old as I am
here.

10:10.141 --> 10:12.360
I have seen this working out.

10:12.360 --> 10:14.150
People are so much changed in their ideas.

10:14.150 --> 10:21.090
There’s such a revolution that you cannot
think [of] a person like Christ, today to

10:21.090 --> 10:23.440
be born and to be crucified.

10:23.440 --> 10:25.160
Of course you may misunderstand.

10:25.160 --> 10:30.880
You may not like Him because He’s a carpenter’s
son, He’s too simple, He talks of spontaneity;

10:30.880 --> 10:33.460
He doesn’t give you any technique; He doesn’t
take any money from you; He doesn’t organise.

10:33.460 --> 10:40.620
You may not like Him, and you may deny Him
also thinking that He’s just useless, but

10:40.620 --> 10:43.610
you cannot crucify [Him].

10:43.610 --> 10:47.360
Under any law you cannot do it.

10:47.360 --> 10:52.750
Imagine what a development of society has
also taken place!

10:52.750 --> 10:54.400
And we understand what is wrong.

10:54.400 --> 10:59.760
For example now, Afghanistan was invaded:
everybody, everyone in the whole world, was

10:59.760 --> 11:02.940
feeling that it was wrong.

11:02.940 --> 11:11.190
When one of the satellites was falling, and
there were some astronauts caught up in that,

11:11.190 --> 11:12.430
the whole world was watching.

11:12.430 --> 11:17.670
I mean, they were not Indians and they were
not Egyptians, but everywhere people were

11:17.670 --> 11:19.980
watching that they should come down safely.

11:19.980 --> 11:25.900
Everybody was praying in their own way that,
“Oh God, they must be safe!”

11:25.900 --> 11:31.740
Because of the development outside we are
so much connected with each other: there’s

11:31.740 --> 11:36.740
such an articulation of our thoughts and our
ideas and our feelings and our sensitivities

11:36.740 --> 11:44.360
that, anything happens in any part of our
country, we do feel, in any part of the world,

11:44.360 --> 11:48.670
we feel; anywhere anything happens to someone,
we feel it.

11:48.670 --> 11:52.680
So our collectivity has also become sharper
and sensitive.

11:52.680 --> 11:56.580
It’s a remarkable time we are born in.

11:56.580 --> 11:58.330
You are very fortunate and lucky people.

11:58.330 --> 12:04.080
And your age group specially is specially
blessed because, at this time, you are well-read,

12:04.080 --> 12:10.080
you know all about it and you are just there
to understand and get it.

12:10.080 --> 12:19.870
But, as I said, that, in a country like India
where, from ancient times, there has been

12:19.870 --> 12:29.250
a big search within, much more known to them
were the truths of life.

12:29.250 --> 12:36.380
They knew what they were seeking, they knew
what they had to seek and what is to expect

12:36.380 --> 12:38.060
in your seeking.

12:38.060 --> 12:44.870
Though I would say India is today sleeping
compared to you people.

12:44.870 --> 12:46.620
You are awake, you are definitely awake.

12:46.620 --> 12:53.010
Those who know what to seek are sleeping;
those who are awake do not know what to seek.

12:53.010 --> 12:55.130
It’s a funny situation!

12:55.130 --> 13:05.279
But we can understand it by understanding
one fact, that, when the tree grows outside

13:05.279 --> 13:11.720
too much we must know that the roots must
have grown down deep, otherwise the tree cannot

13:11.720 --> 13:13.390
be sustained.

13:13.390 --> 13:22.550
If, in the West, we have grown very much outside,
in the East maybe one or two roots, maybe,

13:22.550 --> 13:27.290
have gone deep down to find out the source
to sustain this tree.

13:27.290 --> 13:30.870
For me, east and west doesn’t exit.

13:30.870 --> 13:33.630
Nor does it exist for anything that is Divine.

13:33.630 --> 13:37.400
It’s a human conception of east and west
and these countries and all that.

13:37.400 --> 13:40.520
It’s only one map, a beautiful picture God
has created.

13:40.520 --> 13:43.690
Only human beings think that we are different
and they are different.

13:43.690 --> 13:48.770
Of course He has created varieties just to
create the joy of beauty.

13:48.770 --> 13:56.060
But He never created east, west, north, south
and the difference between the people.

13:56.060 --> 13:57.670
That’s our own conception.

13:57.670 --> 14:05.620
[But], whatever it is, definitely in the growth
there are two types of people: one are the

14:05.620 --> 14:12.030
people who are growing outside, extroversion
is much more, people are seeking outside,

14:12.030 --> 14:17.490
and there are people who are seeking inside.

14:17.490 --> 14:23.310
I would say like the Pisces, you see, they
have two fishes: one fish is seeking inside

14:23.310 --> 14:24.960
and one fish is seeking outside.

14:24.960 --> 14:31.370
In the same way the whole universe looks to
me that some are seeking outside and some

14:31.370 --> 14:33.540
are seeking inside.

14:33.540 --> 14:43.070
Now those who are seekers of the Divine must
take some guidance from people who have found

14:43.070 --> 14:45.040
out something before.

14:45.040 --> 14:51.600
For example, I had a big discussion with a
gentleman who said, “This is occidental

14:51.600 --> 14:53.800
and this is that…” and all.

14:53.800 --> 14:56.270
I asked him, “Who was Christ?

14:56.270 --> 15:00.240
Was He born in England or in America?

15:00.240 --> 15:02.710
Why did you accept Him?”

15:02.710 --> 15:06.540
I mean He has to be born somewhere!

15:06.540 --> 15:09.470
After all, either He’ll be born in the East
or in the West.

15:09.470 --> 15:14.160
Supposing He’s born in the West: so the
Eastern people should say that, “Because

15:14.160 --> 15:16.290
He was born in the West, we’ll reject Him."

15:16.290 --> 15:20.150
He is born in the East so Western people should
say, “We will reject Him because He was

15:20.150 --> 15:21.430
born in the East!”

15:21.430 --> 15:23.730
This is absurd!

15:23.730 --> 15:27.190
I mean, a person can be born in one place
only, he cannot be born everywhere.

15:27.190 --> 15:29.330
He has to be born somewhere.

15:29.330 --> 15:35.770
But these kind of localised identifications
have led to lots of problems in the minds

15:35.770 --> 15:37.250
of people.

15:37.250 --> 15:44.459
As scientists we have to keep our mind very,
very open to understand what search people

15:44.459 --> 15:53.020
have made in the inner being, to find out
what are we made of, why are we here, why

15:53.020 --> 15:57.720
did we get our evolution from amoeba to this
stage, where have we to reach.

15:57.720 --> 16:01.060
We have to understand the other side of the
picture.

16:01.060 --> 16:07.330
And [it’s] much more necessary for people
who are now seeking that which was found out

16:07.330 --> 16:08.330
in the East.

16:08.330 --> 16:13.660
And Eastern people are seeking that which
you have found out here.

16:13.660 --> 16:16.950
They are getting developed, you see, they
are now getting sophisticated.

16:16.950 --> 16:24.270
While you are trying to find out something
which they had found out without much sophistication.

16:24.270 --> 16:34.120
In the ancient times, a long, long time back,
we had three types of people working out the

16:34.120 --> 16:35.120
seeking.

16:35.120 --> 16:41.720
The first type I would say were the people
who were on the left hand side of this Primordial

16:41.720 --> 16:45.910
Being which you see there with a blue line
.

16:45.910 --> 16:49.580
Have you something to show them?

16:49.580 --> 17:01.940
This blue line is the representative of a
channel called Ida Nadi.

17:01.940 --> 17:09.110
And this channel was discovered thousands
of years back in India.

17:09.110 --> 17:14.880
This channel represents the power of desire
within us.

17:14.880 --> 17:23.519
And the desire reached such a subtle form
that there was a desire to meet God, to be

17:23.519 --> 17:28.339
one with your Spirit; that’s the last desire.

17:28.339 --> 17:39.489
And this desire became what you call as the
power of devotion or dedication or for asking,

17:39.489 --> 17:42.070
“Oh Lord, when are we going to meet?

17:42.070 --> 17:49.919
You must come, and we are waiting for You,”
and all such things which shows that people

17:49.919 --> 17:55.740
believed that there was some Superior Power
and that we had to receive the help from that

17:55.740 --> 17:56.740
Superior Power.

17:56.740 --> 18:00.919
This was one side or one type of people who
existed.

18:00.919 --> 18:08.630
And the other side [that] you see is the yellow
line: this is the power of our action.

18:08.630 --> 18:12.460
The channel is called as Pingala channel.

18:12.460 --> 18:17.559
These are all very subtle channels inside
our spinal cord.

18:17.559 --> 18:27.529
This Pingala channel expressed in the people
who went into action.

18:27.529 --> 18:36.369
Now the power of action in the West, I think,
is a later manifestation of the way people

18:36.369 --> 18:38.289
acted in India.

18:38.289 --> 18:45.159
By this power they try to find out the mysteries
of the matter.

18:45.159 --> 18:47.860
As you know matter is made of five elements.

18:47.860 --> 18:55.149
So they wanted to know how to overpower the
matter; how to harness it, how to use it.

18:55.149 --> 19:01.279
And they tried to find out which are the Deities
which are ruling the material side of life.

19:01.279 --> 19:06.389
For example, which is the Deity for the sea,
what is the Deity for water, what is the Deity

19:06.389 --> 19:10.070
for Sun, Moon and other stars, and all those
things.

19:10.070 --> 19:16.690
And Greeks, I think, went further with it,
very much further, and they got into a wrong

19:16.690 --> 19:19.840
path and they got lost.

19:19.840 --> 19:31.509
But this was the search where people tried
to excite or to master the methods by which

19:31.509 --> 19:35.870
you could control all these five elements.

19:35.870 --> 19:39.730
And this method is expressed in our Vedas.

19:39.730 --> 19:48.049
‘Vida’ means ‘to know’; and the Vedas
are the expressions of all the mantras which

19:48.049 --> 19:50.499
were used to harness the matter.

19:50.499 --> 19:57.369
The result of that is, today, what we feel,
is science: that, through that, now science

19:57.369 --> 20:00.669
is manifested as knowledge to us.

20:00.669 --> 20:03.330
But first they tried to, say, overpower the
fire.

20:03.330 --> 20:10.029
Now there is one way of overpowering the fire:
is from outside to use the fire for cooking,

20:10.029 --> 20:12.010
for this, that, all sorts of things.

20:12.010 --> 20:17.470
Or there could be a method by which you find
out the Deity that rules the fire.

20:17.470 --> 20:23.359
If you can excite the Deity that rules the
fire and can control that Deity or you are

20:23.359 --> 20:30.929
connected with that Deity, then you can manage
to use the fire the way you like.

20:30.929 --> 20:35.630
So the second type of people who went into
these mantras and yagyas and all these things:

20:35.630 --> 20:40.080
they did the fire ceremonies and tried to
control the Sun, Moon and all sort of things;

20:40.080 --> 20:42.269
they were interested [in that].

20:42.269 --> 20:50.239
But now the third type of people, who existed
in the centre, in the central path.

20:50.239 --> 20:55.600
This path is called as the Sushumna path,
and this path is responsible for our evolution

20:55.600 --> 20:57.870
from amoeba to this stage.

20:57.870 --> 21:04.600
Because of this power within us, to evolve,
we became human beings.

21:04.600 --> 21:06.279
Why did we become human beings?

21:06.279 --> 21:07.279
Nobody asks!

21:07.279 --> 21:08.279
We should ask some questions!

21:08.279 --> 21:13.580
All the scientists must ask questions [such
as]: Why did we become human beings?

21:13.580 --> 21:18.990
Why some animals were discarded, and why we
are supposed to be on top of all the evolutionary

21:18.990 --> 21:19.990
process?

21:19.990 --> 21:21.120
And now what is our goal?

21:21.120 --> 21:22.929
Why are we there?

21:22.929 --> 21:25.679
What are we to achieve?

21:25.679 --> 21:37.190
This central path is a very, very important
path for us, for Sahaja Yoga, because, by

21:37.190 --> 21:43.269
these different chakras that there are, the
one is the lower one, then the second, the

21:43.269 --> 21:50.359
third and the fourth, fifth, sixth and seventh:
these seven chakras denote vertically our

21:50.359 --> 21:52.330
evolution — vertically.

21:52.330 --> 22:00.460
And horizontally they express our physical,
mental, emotional being.

22:00.460 --> 22:04.899
The first chakra is very important.

22:04.899 --> 22:08.320
This chakra is the centre of Mooladhara.

22:08.320 --> 22:13.220
‘Mooladhara’ means ‘the support of the
root’.

22:13.220 --> 22:17.120
This centre is the centre of our innocence.

22:17.120 --> 22:23.509
The first thing that was created on this Earth
was innocence.

22:23.509 --> 22:28.029
Innocence is the first power that was created.

22:28.029 --> 22:30.580
And that’s what we had to preserve first
of all.

22:30.580 --> 22:34.559
That was the most important thing to preserve:
is our innocence.

22:34.559 --> 22:40.249
Now you will be surprised that this centre
is placed under the Kundalini, not above the

22:40.249 --> 22:41.249
Kundalini.

22:41.249 --> 22:43.330
Kundalini is above that.

22:43.330 --> 22:48.769
Now this Kundalini is the power which is placed
in the sacrum bone, nowhere else.

22:48.769 --> 22:52.950
I mean people can tell you, I have heard the
other day, he was saying, that, “We believe

22:52.950 --> 22:54.230
the Kundalini is here."

22:54.230 --> 22:57.010
I said, “You can believe it, it is here!

22:57.010 --> 22:59.429
I mean, but by believing it is not there!”

22:59.429 --> 23:02.080
Because what you see is the pulsation of Kundalini
in this area.

23:02.080 --> 23:06.480
When Sahaja Yoga starts, in many people, with
the naked eyes, you can see the pulsation

23:06.480 --> 23:12.330
of the Kundalini in this area, on people who
have got some obstruction.

23:12.330 --> 23:14.759
Those who are all right they just get their
Realisation without any difficulties.

23:14.759 --> 23:17.880
But [with] those who have obstruction, many
of you have seen the pulsation in the sacrum

23:17.880 --> 23:18.880
bone.

23:18.880 --> 23:20.889
And imagine this bone is called ‘sacrum’!

23:20.889 --> 23:22.239
‘Sacrum’ means ‘sacred’.

23:22.239 --> 23:25.520
So they knew that there was something in it.

23:25.520 --> 23:27.119
Even the Greeks, I think.

23:27.119 --> 23:30.010
Latin is not Greek, but we can say in Latin
language it is called as sacred.

23:30.010 --> 23:37.640
So the sacred bone was containing this Sacred
Power within us known as ‘Kundalini’.

23:37.640 --> 23:42.539
This is the primule, is the germinating power
within us.

23:42.539 --> 23:50.669
Now this fact has been accepted for thousands
of years in India and elsewhere.

23:50.669 --> 23:58.559
In the Bible also it is said that Moses saw
the tree of fire.

23:58.559 --> 24:02.179
That tree of fire is nothing but the whole
Kundalini instrument.

24:02.179 --> 24:10.279
They talk of the Tree of Life: that is the
same as this.

24:10.279 --> 24:13.559
In the Bible it is said, “I will appear
before you like tongues of flames,” [this]

24:13.559 --> 24:14.879
is nothing but these centres.

24:14.879 --> 24:20.080
And these centres, you can see clearly within
yourself, look like living flames as these

24:20.080 --> 24:21.080
are.

24:21.080 --> 24:23.960
But these are static, and they are moving
and living.

24:23.960 --> 24:31.289
So this is the thing that is being described
in our ancient books, in all the scriptures.

24:31.289 --> 24:34.529
Even in Koran they have described as ‘Ruh’,
R-U-H, ‘Ruh’.

24:34.529 --> 24:39.259
‘Ruh’ means the cool breeze, the cool
breeze.

24:39.259 --> 24:44.989
The Cool Breeze of the Holy Ghost is described
in the Bible also.

24:44.989 --> 24:47.919
You cannot suddenly start a new idea about
something.

24:47.919 --> 24:54.909
If it is an evolutionary process, if it is
a living process, it must have its background,

24:54.909 --> 24:59.000
its history and it must culminate into something
fruitful.

24:59.000 --> 25:02.769
Like every fruit has a tree behind it and
roots behind it.

25:02.769 --> 25:06.029
You cannot just come out from somewhere and
say, “See now, I have created a fruit!

25:06.029 --> 25:07.890
Now this fruit can become like this."

25:07.890 --> 25:09.590
It has no meaning.

25:09.590 --> 25:12.130
It must be a plastic fruit.

25:12.130 --> 25:13.379
It cannot be a real fruit.

25:13.379 --> 25:17.299
If it is a living fruit it has to come out
of the tree.

25:17.299 --> 25:22.539
That has existed for thousands and thousands
of years and out of that this tree has to

25:22.539 --> 25:23.539
come.

25:23.539 --> 25:24.610
It must have the base.

25:24.610 --> 25:28.320
And this is traditionally called as the Kundalini
awakening process.

25:28.320 --> 25:34.809
Now, this was done, as I told you, there was
only one person at the time of Rama, Nachiketa

25:34.809 --> 25:35.840
who tried to find it.

25:35.840 --> 25:40.429
Yoga Vasishtha was a realised-soul, no doubt,
but he did not give Realisation to anyone.

25:40.429 --> 25:44.279
Only Raja Janaka gave Realisation to one fellow
called Nachiketa.

25:44.279 --> 25:51.109
Even Zen system in which people were supposed
to get their Realisation: they said that nobody

25:51.109 --> 25:55.340
got Realisation except that there were twenty-six
kashyapas.

25:55.340 --> 25:57.740
‘Kashyapas’ means “realised-souls”.

25:57.740 --> 26:02.470
Only twenty-six, because I think it started
about the sixth century.

26:02.470 --> 26:08.109
And for six centuries they had these kashyapas
coming and going, one at a time.

26:08.109 --> 26:11.340
And after that they had none, they had none.

26:11.340 --> 26:15.929
So there are no realised-souls there either.

26:15.929 --> 26:20.509
Christ has said very clearly that, “You
are to be born again."

26:20.509 --> 26:25.149
I mean the whole message of Christ’s life
is Realisation.

26:25.149 --> 26:34.539
Because Judaism talked of the dharma, of the
sustenance, of maintenance of the balance

26:34.539 --> 26:36.820
in the centre.

26:36.820 --> 26:40.049
That also, like a tree, that was very important.

26:40.049 --> 26:47.850
But then Christ came on this Earth to show
that you have to become the Spirit.

26:47.850 --> 26:51.590
By His resurrection He showed that.

26:51.590 --> 26:53.320
And this is the message of Christ.

26:53.320 --> 26:57.019
But in Christianity, I don’t know how many
people are seeking.

26:57.019 --> 27:00.299
They think that by going to church every morning
it’s finished.

27:00.299 --> 27:08.210
Same with the Indians where it was said in
every scripture, even about Vedas the first

27:08.210 --> 27:14.080
thing is said that, “Through this knowledge
if you cannot seek your Spirit, it’s all

27:14.080 --> 27:15.080
useless."

27:15.080 --> 27:19.830
Then we had people like Shankaracharya, Adi
Shankaracharya, who was the person who tried

27:19.830 --> 27:22.039
to re-establish Hinduism.

27:22.039 --> 27:25.029
Who has said that, “Without getting Realisation,
what’s this life?”

27:25.029 --> 27:26.029
“Na yogye, na sankhye."

27:26.029 --> 27:29.889
(meaning: neither by ‘yoga’ nor ‘sankhya’
it is achieved’) By all this talking, blah,

27:29.889 --> 27:31.542
blah blahs, where are you going to lie?

27:31.542 --> 27:35.659
You have to get the grace of the Mother to
get your Realisation.

27:35.659 --> 27:42.049
When he talked first of ‘Vivekachudamani’,
a very big book he wrote, on treaties of Indian

27:42.049 --> 27:45.149
philosophy, people were amazed at his knowledge.

27:45.149 --> 27:50.159
But later on he just wrote ‘Saundarya Lahari’
which is just the description of the Cool

27:50.159 --> 27:52.519
Breeze of the Holy Ghost and of the Holy Ghost.

27:52.519 --> 27:54.029
And people said, “What are you doing?

27:54.029 --> 27:57.070
You are just praising the Holy Ghost and not
writing any philosophy."

27:57.070 --> 27:59.009
He said, “There is no philosophy.

27:59.009 --> 28:04.460
It’s a spontaneous thing which should happen
to all of us, and just the praise is the way

28:04.460 --> 28:05.460
you get it."

28:05.460 --> 28:07.529
Just imagine a person of his calibre.

28:07.529 --> 28:13.700
But what are the Hindus doing today is nothing
but the same old-style techniques and ritualism

28:13.700 --> 28:16.379
and all nonsense; they are also lost.

28:16.379 --> 28:26.020
I mean there is such a pickle, made out of
every great incarnation, that to me it was

28:26.020 --> 28:33.559
a shock to see how they have been able to
spoil every incarnation into zero, and some

28:33.559 --> 28:41.919
sort of a nonsensical image of every incarnation
who came on this Earth to emancipate, to give

28:41.919 --> 28:45.509
you a higher life, a higher awareness.

28:45.509 --> 28:50.720
So we come to the point where we have to think
what we have to expect.

28:50.720 --> 28:56.470
The first thing is: if it is a living process,
it has to be spontaneous.

28:56.470 --> 29:05.580
This is very difficult for people to understand:
that it has to be spontaneous.

29:05.580 --> 29:13.140
For example, if this flower has to become
the fruit, what is the technique?

29:13.140 --> 29:19.149
Do you stand before it for hours together
or do you jump before it, or you stand on

29:19.149 --> 29:23.529
your heads [so] that it becomes?

29:23.529 --> 29:29.229
Anything spontaneous [that] you have seen,
which is living, happens by itself.

29:29.229 --> 29:30.999
There is no technique.

29:30.999 --> 29:35.149
When I say there is no technique, people do
not want to believe it, because technique

29:35.149 --> 29:36.149
they want.

29:36.149 --> 29:40.759
But you have taken for granted all these things,
isn’t it?

29:40.759 --> 29:47.200
I mean, one day you are sleeping, you find
that the blossom time has come, lots of flowers

29:47.200 --> 29:48.399
are there.

29:48.399 --> 29:52.769
One morning you get up you find most of the
flowers have become fruits, and you take it

29:52.769 --> 29:53.769
for granted.

29:53.769 --> 29:56.419
Do you ask for a technique there?

29:56.419 --> 30:00.239
In the same way what technique did you employ
to become human beings from amoeba?

30:00.239 --> 30:04.399
Say from monkey’s state to human beings:
did you cut your tails to become human beings?

30:04.399 --> 30:07.741
Didn’t we become spontaneously that?

30:07.741 --> 30:08.741
It’s rather difficult to accept.

30:08.741 --> 30:13.700
But logically, you tell me, if it is a living
process, what do we have do?

30:13.700 --> 30:20.179
It is impossible to explain to people that
there is no technique.

30:20.179 --> 30:22.200
They must have a technique.

30:22.200 --> 30:27.870
Now why do we want to have a technique?Let
us face ourselves.

30:27.870 --> 30:33.229
Because we think we must do something about
it: if we are not doing anything about it,

30:33.229 --> 30:34.899
then how can we get it?

30:34.899 --> 30:40.529
Because we think whatever we have got in this
world is through our effort, by working for

30:40.529 --> 30:41.529
it.

30:41.529 --> 30:42.529
But what have you got?

30:42.529 --> 30:43.529
You’ve got everything dead!

30:43.529 --> 30:44.529
Say for example, something is dead, these
stones are dead and you have made a building

30:44.529 --> 30:46.110
out of it.

30:46.110 --> 30:47.159
So what?

30:47.159 --> 30:48.879
Dead from the dead!

30:48.879 --> 30:53.129
What have you got living with you?

30:53.129 --> 30:55.690
Have you got any living powers?

30:55.690 --> 30:59.599
Can you give life to a fruit or to a tree?

30:59.599 --> 31:01.730
You cannot.

31:01.730 --> 31:02.730
What have you achieved?

31:02.730 --> 31:03.730
Is only dead.

31:03.730 --> 31:05.259
With effort you can only achieve dead.

31:05.259 --> 31:08.179
Have you achieved anything living?

31:08.179 --> 31:13.259
If you put such a question to yourself then
you will understand that living processes,

31:13.259 --> 31:19.840
we have to accept, are spontaneous: we cannot
put any technique on it.

31:19.840 --> 31:27.659
As soon as we want to have technique, we must
know this is our Mr Ego who wants to get satisfied.

31:27.659 --> 31:30.590
I have seen people doing that.

31:30.590 --> 31:37.190
For example I will give you a very concrete
example of a gentleman who came to me and

31:37.190 --> 31:38.190
he said, “No, no.

31:38.190 --> 31:39.190
How can be it that be simple Mother?

31:39.190 --> 31:40.190
How can it be that simple?”

31:40.190 --> 31:44.499
I told him that, “See: your breathing is
so simple.

31:44.499 --> 31:47.879
If you have to read books and go into techniques
for your breathing, how many people would

31:47.879 --> 31:49.080
be living?”

31:49.080 --> 31:50.349
But he would not accept me.

31:50.349 --> 31:52.779
He said, “You must give us a technique otherwise
we’ll not be happy."

31:52.779 --> 31:59.379
Now there’s a very great realised-soul living
in India but he is a very strict person, he’s

31:59.379 --> 32:01.899
not a Mother and he has no tolerance for any
nonsense.

32:01.899 --> 32:06.290
So he had once told me, “If somebody troubles
you, send the fellow over to me."

32:06.290 --> 32:07.290
So I told him, “You go and see the guruji,
such and such."

32:07.290 --> 32:10.149
He was very enamoured that, “This gentleman
has called me!”

32:10.149 --> 32:16.599
So he had to climb up seven miles up on a
hill where this gentleman was sitting there.

32:16.599 --> 32:21.029
He went there, and he started talking, “Blah,
blah, blah,” to him that, “See, Mother

32:21.029 --> 32:24.609
doesn’t give any technique to us and She’s
just giving Realisation to every Dick, Tom

32:24.609 --> 32:25.639
and Harry and this and that!”

32:25.639 --> 32:26.639
He said, “Yah!

32:26.639 --> 32:27.950
Really, She’s doing wrong, isn’t it?

32:27.950 --> 32:31.140
All right, you be here and you eat your food
and sleep here!”

32:31.140 --> 32:37.210
After a month I found the gentleman came to
see me with both his legs round his neck,

32:37.210 --> 32:38.450
dangling in the air.

32:38.450 --> 32:41.169
I said, “What’s happened?”

32:41.169 --> 32:44.110
I mean, really tears came into my eyes and
I said, “What’s happened?

32:44.110 --> 32:47.169
What this guru has done to him?”

32:47.169 --> 32:48.289
He came and started crying.

32:48.289 --> 32:49.739
He said, “Mother, never send me to that
guru."

32:49.739 --> 32:54.190
I said, “But you were very anxious to go
to him, because you wanted something to climb

32:54.190 --> 32:55.190
up to see him."

32:55.190 --> 32:58.719
He said, “He made really a mess out of me."

32:58.719 --> 33:03.129
In the night because this guru, his limbs
are broken and hands are broken, so he goes

33:03.129 --> 33:04.129
on a tiger.

33:04.129 --> 33:06.940
So he said, “And this tiger came and pushed
me into a ghat!

33:06.940 --> 33:12.840
And I was lying there about thirteen, fourteen
feet down below, and this guru after three,

33:12.840 --> 33:19.749
four days lowered down some rotis, some breads
to me, and he said, “Now eat it and stay

33:19.749 --> 33:20.749
there.

33:20.749 --> 33:24.229
And till you promise me that you will not
go and trouble Mataji, I am not going to take

33:24.229 --> 33:26.169
you out of this place!”

33:26.169 --> 33:29.919
And then after two days he sent a few people
to pick him up and brought.

33:29.919 --> 33:33.590
He said, “I am not here to take money from
you.

33:33.590 --> 33:35.289
You cannot give me money, anything.

33:35.289 --> 33:37.249
But I will only teach you a good lesson!”

33:37.249 --> 33:39.389
He said, “I have had enough of it."

33:39.389 --> 33:43.759
He said, “Now you take these legs around
your neck, go dangling to Mataji, and She’s

33:43.759 --> 33:44.929
going to cure you.

33:44.929 --> 33:46.369
I am not going to cure you.

33:46.369 --> 33:48.950
And don’t come and tell me stories!”

33:48.950 --> 33:52.349
“Oh God” I said, “Look at this,” then
of course we tried and worked on him, that’s

33:52.349 --> 33:53.349
a different point.

33:53.349 --> 33:54.349
But this is what it is.

33:54.349 --> 33:57.519
He said he wants technique, so he gave him
a technique.

33:57.519 --> 34:03.080
Another fellow who was like this, a doctor,
he was troubling me, and I didn’t tell him,

34:03.080 --> 34:05.549
but he felt that he should go and see this
guru.

34:05.549 --> 34:10.270
And for one month he made this fellow clean
a Shiva’s temple, taking the water seven

34:10.270 --> 34:13.750
miles every day, morning and evening: with
one bucket cleaning in Shiva’s temple!

34:13.750 --> 34:17.810
And doctor came back, he was so thinned down,
absolutely exhausted.

34:17.810 --> 34:20.629
I said, “What’s the matter?”

34:20.629 --> 34:23.059
He said, “I was cleaning Shiva’s temple
for a month!”

34:23.059 --> 34:26.639
So when I met this guru I asked him, “Why
did you do that to him?”

34:26.639 --> 34:27.990
He said, “For a donkey, you better give
donkey’s job!

34:27.990 --> 34:29.620
It’s no use telling them something of the
higher life.

34:29.620 --> 34:32.070
They don’t want it.

34:32.070 --> 34:34.510
They want donkey’s life.

34:34.510 --> 34:39.659
So let them jump and do what they like.

34:39.659 --> 34:42.299
Let them be donkeys.

34:42.299 --> 34:45.990
Why should You try to give them [everything]
so simple?”

34:45.990 --> 34:46.990
I was amazed at him.

34:46.990 --> 34:49.560
He said, “Mother, you are a Mother and you
do what you like because this is your whim.

34:49.560 --> 34:52.799
But as far as we are concerned we are not
going to give Realisation to anyone.

34:52.799 --> 34:55.129
I have given it to one, and he’s become
a hopeless man."

34:55.129 --> 35:02.150
So I went to see this gentleman one day, the
one who took twenty-five years to get his

35:02.150 --> 35:03.150
Realisation.

35:03.150 --> 35:06.440
And because somebody, one of my disciples
had to invite him.

35:06.440 --> 35:11.170
Now this fellow was smoking cigarettes like
this, sitting before me and he was talking

35:11.170 --> 35:16.599
quite a lot, and there were girls and women
pressing his feet and doing all kinds of things.

35:16.599 --> 35:19.170
Of course he got up, touched my feet.

35:19.170 --> 35:23.240
He sat down, then he started saying that,
“Now why this [Gagangiri] Maharaj is coming

35:23.240 --> 35:24.730
to see you in Bombay?

35:24.730 --> 35:26.240
After all he should not leave his place.

35:26.240 --> 35:29.059
He has been there for a hundred and eight
years,” this, that.

35:29.059 --> 35:32.740
I said, “Who are you to judge him?

35:32.740 --> 35:33.780
Why are you judging him?

35:33.780 --> 35:34.780
He’s your guru.

35:34.780 --> 35:35.780
Why should you judge him?

35:35.780 --> 35:36.780
He has given you Realisation."

35:36.780 --> 35:37.780
“Yes, yes, he’s given me Realisation,
I know.

35:37.780 --> 35:38.780
But I can also tell him something."

35:38.780 --> 35:39.930
I said, “But what about your smoking?

35:39.930 --> 35:41.160
You are still on with the smoking."

35:41.160 --> 35:42.630
“Oh, I don’t care.

35:42.630 --> 35:44.090
I am beyond everything!”

35:44.090 --> 35:45.560
I said, “All right."

35:45.560 --> 35:48.540
Then I sat down watching him for a while.

35:48.540 --> 35:52.920
I said, “Now I am going home."

35:52.920 --> 35:53.920
I said, “You apply this tika to me."

35:53.920 --> 35:55.630
I said, “All right, first I will apply,”
so I applied [to] him.

35:55.630 --> 36:00.240
I said, “Now you apply,” and I sucked
his finger, this is Agnya’s finger of ego.

36:00.240 --> 36:05.060
I sucked his finger on my Agnya, and he went
on “Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha!” like that.

36:05.060 --> 36:06.060
He said, “Mother, Mother, Mother what you
are doing?”

36:06.060 --> 36:08.420
I said, “Nothing, nothing.

36:08.420 --> 36:10.170
You are great, you are a realised-soul.

36:10.170 --> 36:11.710
Why should you shake before me?

36:11.710 --> 36:12.740
Why are you shaking?

36:12.740 --> 36:13.849
Why don’t you get all right?

36:13.849 --> 36:14.849
Why are you shaking?”

36:14.849 --> 36:16.420
He said, “No, no, no please stop it, stop
it."

36:16.420 --> 36:21.119
I said, “Now, first promise that you are
not going to talk ill of your guru and stop

36:21.119 --> 36:24.299
all this nonsense of having women around and
making money!”

36:24.299 --> 36:29.799
But then the person with whom he went, he
swindled them completely, just imagine!

36:29.799 --> 36:35.180
And I asked this gentleman who met me at the
airport, “Why did you give money to this

36:35.180 --> 36:36.180
man?”

36:36.180 --> 36:39.920
They said, “Mother, because he said, ‘See,
I was shaking before Mother because I was

36:39.920 --> 36:40.920
giving power to Her!’”

36:40.920 --> 36:41.920
I said, “Such fools!

36:41.920 --> 36:42.920
Why did you give him the money?

36:42.920 --> 36:45.200
Why didn’t you ask me what was happening?”

36:45.200 --> 36:48.819
This is what it is.

36:48.819 --> 36:55.010
When you want technique, then in the market
there are thousand and one to give you technique,

36:55.010 --> 36:56.010
anything.

36:56.010 --> 36:59.200
They may tell you that put this [candle] on
your head, light this, and walk on the street.

36:59.200 --> 37:01.779
And you will find thousands of them walking
like this, and the price of this [candle]

37:01.779 --> 37:05.650
will go up in the market, and people will
be doing it.

37:05.650 --> 37:12.309
Any sort of nonsense they will give you, they
would like to do it!

37:12.309 --> 37:18.940
For example, these people at Oxford Street:
they are standing there, [the] Hareramas.

37:18.940 --> 37:25.430
They had cleaned their hair completely and
applied those, what we call them shendis in

37:25.430 --> 37:27.530
India, I don’t know what you call.

37:27.530 --> 37:30.990
And they are sold in the market; do you know?

37:30.990 --> 37:32.920
Like all other wigs, they are sold as wigs
there, and that is to applied there.

37:32.920 --> 37:33.920
And when they were dancing that was falling
down, you know!

37:33.920 --> 37:38.599
And the dress and sari they were wearing was
also falling down!

37:38.599 --> 37:40.359
And such foolish people.

37:40.359 --> 37:41.980
I said, “What do they think?

37:41.980 --> 37:44.830
By doing this, are they going to get God?”

37:44.830 --> 37:52.140
I said, “But why don’t you sit down and
receive the blessings and why to do [this]?”

37:52.140 --> 37:54.380
They said, “But what’s wrong in clothes.

37:54.380 --> 37:55.570
What is the need to have clothes?”

37:55.570 --> 37:56.750
I said, “That’s not the point!

37:56.750 --> 38:03.329
What I am saying if by becoming naked, if
you can become God, all the animals must go

38:03.329 --> 38:05.430
to God first, before you!”

