You must understand what should happen to
you: is there should be a new dimension which

38:08.980 --> 38:09.980
must be enlightened within you.

38:09.980 --> 38:15.450
A new dimension must come into you.

38:15.450 --> 38:18.630
What about your own power: have you got you
own powers?

38:18.630 --> 38:22.260
If you are spiritually evolved, you must have
your own powers.

38:22.260 --> 38:24.529
This is like enslavement.

38:24.529 --> 38:25.529
I said, “What are our own powers?”

38:25.529 --> 38:28.780
I said, “Can you tell in this person where
is the Kundalini?”

38:28.780 --> 38:30.160
They said, “No, we don’t know.

38:30.160 --> 38:31.569
We have never heard about it."

38:31.569 --> 38:33.599
“Can you tell what are your centres catching?

38:33.599 --> 38:35.200
Can you tell where are his centres rising?”

38:35.200 --> 38:36.980
He said, “No, we cannot."

38:36.980 --> 38:41.880
So I called him, I said, “Come along, have
your Realisation."

38:41.880 --> 38:44.710
One of them I got hold of, somehow or other
brought him.

38:44.710 --> 38:47.270
I think he was not interested in Realisation
at all.

38:47.270 --> 38:49.270
He was not at all interested.

38:49.270 --> 38:52.089
He was interested in exhibitionism.

38:52.089 --> 38:55.000
He wanted to exhibition himself in that Oxford
Street that’s why he went there.

38:55.000 --> 38:56.000
Absolutely that’s true.

38:56.000 --> 38:57.359
Otherwise, if he was, he would have said,
“All right, if you are saying ‘I am giving

38:57.359 --> 38:59.690
you Realisation,’ let me have it!”

38:59.690 --> 39:03.220
He said, “How can that be so silly?”

39:03.220 --> 39:04.220
I said, “What silly?

39:04.220 --> 39:08.270
I said, “How can it be silly?”

39:08.270 --> 39:09.859
I said, “The wisest”.

39:09.859 --> 39:14.340
But must be somebody else is silly to see
things which are silly.

39:14.340 --> 39:17.180
Like mad people: if you go to a lunatic asylum
they think you all are mad.

39:17.180 --> 39:24.920
Once our prime minister went to a lunatic
asylum and one lunatic came and started talking

39:24.920 --> 39:25.920
to him very nicely.

39:25.920 --> 39:26.920
He said, “How are you?

39:26.920 --> 39:28.330
When did you come here?

39:28.330 --> 39:29.330
And who are you?”

39:29.330 --> 39:31.900
So he said, “I am Jawaharlal Nehru, I am
the prime minister of India."

39:31.900 --> 39:33.829
He said, “All right, all right, you’ll
be all right also.

39:33.829 --> 39:38.170
I used to say the same thing."

39:38.170 --> 39:39.440
(laughter)

39:39.440 --> 39:43.549
But how do you judge whether you are right
or wrong?

39:43.549 --> 39:44.950
Where are you?

39:44.950 --> 39:50.190
The judgment comes when you have the dimension
to judge.

39:50.190 --> 39:52.260
When you are Realised you can judge.

39:52.260 --> 39:54.589
You can say what chakras are catching.

39:54.589 --> 39:59.760
When Self-realisation comes in, you know all
about these centres and you know all about

39:59.760 --> 40:01.880
these channels; about yourself and about others.

40:01.880 --> 40:06.039
The collective consciousness becomes an actualisation;
it becomes part and parcel of you.

40:06.039 --> 40:10.720
Like an egg when it gets transformed, you
really get a bird!

40:10.720 --> 40:14.410
It’s not just “blah, blah, blah."

40:14.410 --> 40:18.930
You just get to see the bird with its wings
and everything.

40:18.930 --> 40:21.359
A transformation takes place.

40:21.359 --> 40:28.089
Your awareness must have that actual dimension
within itself, inside.

40:28.089 --> 40:33.430
Not outside by developing your some sort of
a horn or wearing some sort of a bushy hair.

40:33.430 --> 40:38.789
It’s something that happens to you within
where…(break in recording)…comes through

40:38.789 --> 40:42.650
when you start judging yourself.

40:42.650 --> 40:45.740
But God is compassion.

40:45.740 --> 40:47.289
He’s love.

40:47.289 --> 40:55.119
He gives you [the] chance, all the powers
to clear yourself and cleanse yourself.

40:55.119 --> 41:03.480
But nobody can help a person who is so dump
founded or mesmerised or who is such a, I

41:03.480 --> 41:09.290
would say, unintelligent person; who doesn’t
understand that something has to happen to

41:09.290 --> 41:12.460
your awareness.

41:12.460 --> 41:14.190
Then only you have achieved something.

41:14.190 --> 41:21.430
For days in and days out they are going and
going and going and achieving nothing.

41:21.430 --> 41:24.119
Somebody told me, “Oh, they are people who
love each other very much."

41:24.119 --> 41:25.119
“How do you know?”

41:25.119 --> 41:26.890
“They kiss each other quite a lot."

41:26.890 --> 41:28.319
I said, “What is there?”

41:28.319 --> 41:30.869
Any licentious society you find such kissing
going on.

41:30.869 --> 41:36.940
For example if you go to France, I mean, it’s
horrifyingly kissing society, I tell you.

41:36.940 --> 41:39.500
Everybody has a right to kiss everyone they
feel like.

41:39.500 --> 41:42.079
I mean, it’s sometimes so much that you
really get frightened of the whole thing:

41:42.079 --> 41:44.589
anybody can come and kiss you, anybody is
supposed to…

41:44.589 --> 41:46.200
I mean, I don’t know how it works out but
it’s so.

41:46.200 --> 41:47.200
So I said, “What is, so [great] in kissing?

41:47.200 --> 41:48.200
There’s no love!”

41:48.200 --> 41:57.990
Love is a thing which is not expressed in
that way, but which works, which flows.

41:57.990 --> 42:03.200
It’s a power which acts, just like the sun’s
rays.

42:03.200 --> 42:05.619
Sun’s rays come and act on the leaves.

42:05.619 --> 42:13.299
In the same way the love flows and acts on
the Kundalini, and it gives Realisation to

42:13.299 --> 42:14.299
others.

42:14.299 --> 42:16.519
It transforms your life.

42:16.519 --> 42:18.980
You become a different person altogether.

42:18.980 --> 42:22.529
You become a master of yourself when you overpower
everything.

42:22.529 --> 42:29.950
Of course some are, I would call them, lame
people, so they need little more time.

42:29.950 --> 42:33.530
Some are very fast ones and some are so quick
that they once get it, they never lose it.

42:33.530 --> 42:41.890
And then the real growth of the new personality
starts in which you start enjoying that bliss

42:41.890 --> 42:43.089
which is promised.

42:43.089 --> 42:46.690
All that is said before has to be proved today
— every thing.

42:46.690 --> 42:55.410
Now like we went to one of the Protestant
Church meeting.

42:55.410 --> 42:57.880
I mean Catholics and Protestants and all sorts
of things, you know!

42:57.880 --> 43:01.130
I am facing, mullahs and priests and this
and that.

43:01.130 --> 43:02.890
But these people they said, “We believe
in Christ."

43:02.890 --> 43:03.890
I said, “Very good!

43:03.890 --> 43:07.490
That’s a very good thing to do, is to believe
in Christ, thank God.

43:07.490 --> 43:13.250
At least there is no anarchist or somebody
who is anti-Christ I am facing here!

43:13.250 --> 43:15.320
But,” I said, “where is Christ?”

43:15.320 --> 43:16.320
“He’s everywhere."

43:16.320 --> 43:17.390
I said, “All right.

43:17.390 --> 43:18.960
But how do you contact Him?”

43:18.960 --> 43:25.500
Everywhere there is ether, everywhere there
are pictures, everywhere there is music, but

43:25.500 --> 43:29.339
how do you get them in the television?

43:29.339 --> 43:30.539
How do you contact?

43:30.539 --> 43:37.450
He is placed in a centre within us and we
can prove it, through the Kundalini awakening,

43:37.450 --> 43:39.230
that Christ is there.

43:39.230 --> 43:44.460
Because when Kundalini reaches that centre,
the centre which is on the optic thalamus,

43:44.460 --> 43:49.789
which controls the pituitary and the pineal
body, [that], in that centre, resides Christ

43:49.789 --> 43:51.650
can be proved through Kundalini awakening.

43:51.650 --> 43:57.150
Because when Kundalini arrives at that point
and it does not pierce, you have to take the

43:57.150 --> 43:59.700
name of Christ and then Kundalini moves on.

43:59.700 --> 44:04.099
But not the person who is not realised, the
one who is realised can only do it.

44:04.099 --> 44:08.480
So there are two types of people you find
in Sahaja Yoga, is the people who are realised

44:08.480 --> 44:10.579
and those who are not realised.

44:10.579 --> 44:14.839
Now here the conflict starts that people who
are realised can shock other people because

44:14.839 --> 44:16.319
they say some things very positively.

44:16.319 --> 44:21.180
They say that, “See, this is wrong, you
should give up these things.

44:21.180 --> 44:23.550
This is not going to lead you anywhere."

44:23.550 --> 44:27.369
And they look just like as you are but they
know about your chakras.

44:27.369 --> 44:31.280
And when they tell you, you get angry with
them and half of them leave, but that’s

44:31.280 --> 44:32.280
not the way.

44:32.280 --> 44:33.690
One should know that they are just trying
to help you.

44:33.690 --> 44:37.339
They were just the same as you were.

44:37.339 --> 44:41.690
Maybe even worse than you were or maybe much
worse than you were but today they have reached

44:41.690 --> 44:44.980
the place from where they can feel you.

44:44.980 --> 44:49.801
And you are also going to do the same, so
there is nothing to be shocked about or to

44:49.801 --> 44:50.870
be angry with.

44:50.870 --> 44:58.809
But there’s tremendous difference in any
artificial type of technique and the real

44:58.809 --> 45:01.109
is this that they know what it is.

