gentleman catching?

45:13.099 --> 45:17.450
They will show the same finger.

45:17.450 --> 45:24.849
And this is such a subjective thing, such
a thing as your own, which has no whims, nothing.

45:24.849 --> 45:26.539
It’s absolutely definite.

