47:15.480 --> 47:19.369
seat of the Spirit, which is manifested in
the heart.

47:19.369 --> 47:23.549
These are the areas, of course doctors don’t
know.

47:23.549 --> 47:29.819
But whatever the psychologists start talking
like blind people can be easily seen through

47:29.819 --> 47:31.940
when the lights are on.

