On the right hand side are the people who
are very ambitious, who dealt with material

48:02.559 --> 48:07.849
things and who try to overpower matter and
tried all kinds of tricks.

48:07.849 --> 48:11.950
These are the people who are still there existing
within us.

48:11.950 --> 48:18.240
When we try to go to the extremes, either
to the left or to the right, by any one of

48:18.240 --> 48:20.559
these techniques, we get caught up.

48:20.559 --> 48:27.140
And when this thing happens, these proteins,
so-called ’58 protein’ and number some

48:27.140 --> 48:31.430
sort of 56, all these are nothing but they
are entities.

48:31.430 --> 48:35.569
They attack us and they trigger the cancer
within us.

48:35.569 --> 48:40.539
And once this is triggered there is no way
out because once you are in these areas, you’ll

48:40.539 --> 48:47.500
be attacked more and more, and the galloping
state is established.

