50:01.220 --> 50:07.569
cells for the use of the brain and it neglects
the spleen, the liver, the pancreas, the kidneys

50:07.569 --> 50:08.569
and the uterus.

50:08.569 --> 50:15.210
But when it neglects the spleen, this is the
first cause [of blood cancer], the primal

50:15.210 --> 50:17.579
cause we can call it.

50:17.579 --> 50:22.190
Secondly, those people who are supposed to
be very speedy — those who think too much

50:22.190 --> 50:23.980
are speedy people also.

