50:48.190 --> 50:53.599
Then they will eat with that speed and immediately
finishing that plate there and they run off

50:53.599 --> 50:54.599
for some other work.

50:54.599 --> 51:00.609
Now this poor spleen has to now create blood
for the digestion, then suddenly the fellow

51:00.609 --> 51:05.089
runs out [so] it has to give the blood cells
for it’s running.

51:05.089 --> 51:08.690
Then he sits down and he starts thinking.

51:08.690 --> 51:10.500
While running he is thinking.

51:10.500 --> 51:12.109
He is doing many things.

51:12.109 --> 51:17.610
We think our body is a multipurpose machine.

51:17.610 --> 51:21.640
So with one thing we will be brushing, with
another thing we will be doing something else,

51:21.640 --> 51:26.089
with ears we will be doing something else,
with nose we will be doing something else,

51:26.089 --> 51:27.940
with stomach we will be doing something else.

51:27.940 --> 51:33.549
Like that, the whole body is poor thing busy
with multipurpose things: poor this body.

51:33.549 --> 51:36.440
