51:36.440 --> 51:39.339
It goes bizarre, as you call it.

51:39.339 --> 51:42.369
It does not know what is wrong with the fellow.

51:42.369 --> 51:48.230
It does not know when it will jump and when
it will go into some sort of a new activity.

51:48.230 --> 51:55.769
So it goes really bizarre, and then the cells
that are created by it become malignant cells,

51:55.769 --> 51:59.160
and blood cancer is settled.

51:59.160 --> 52:06.680
But the third thing that really, that really,
