54:54.950 --> 54:55.950
He was a doctor.

54:55.950 --> 54:59.160
I said, “Doctor, I will be thankful you
come in my place.

54:59.160 --> 55:04.150
Here I am, I have to work till two o’clock
in the night.

55:04.150 --> 55:05.369
I have to work so very hard, such a thankless
job.

55:05.369 --> 55:06.369
You better do it!

55:06.369 --> 55:07.369
I’ll be very happy to be your disciple!

55:07.369 --> 55:08.960
And whatever you say, I am willing to do.

55:08.960 --> 55:11.200
You awaken the Kundalini of people!”

55:11.200 --> 55:13.299
He said, “But I cannot."

55:13.299 --> 55:15.830
So I said, “That’s why I am here!”

55:15.830 --> 55:17.499
Unluckily I know this!

55:17.499 --> 55:19.569
Unfortunately I know it!

55:19.569 --> 55:20.960
Now what to do?

55:20.960 --> 55:22.500
That I am supposed to do.

55:22.500 --> 55:24.950
Now you are supposed to do many things which
